what does best mean.

00:04:51.890 --> 00:04:56.190
Well, best is going to mean --
in our minimization problems,

00:04:56.190 --> 00:05:00.730
it will be the combination
that gives the minimum.

00:05:00.730 --> 00:05:05.760
