piecewise parabolas,

00:05:24.270 --> 00:05:26.790
piecewise cubics, whatever.

00:05:26.790 --> 00:05:29.240
That was the brilliant
finite element idea,

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:32.030
to choose simple functions.

00:05:32.030 --> 00:05:36.080
And then you could
take N quite large,

00:05:36.080 --> 00:05:39.490
