problem and we

00:06:27.780 --> 00:06:32.610
cut its size in half or in
quarter or in eighth, again.

00:06:32.610 --> 00:06:36.750
So projection is producing
a smaller problem,

00:06:36.750 --> 00:06:40.580
and the question is
what are you losing?

00:06:40.580 --> 00:06:42.330
